ecere-sdk (0.44.01-0ubuntu1.1) quantal; urgency=low

  * Fixed issue with 'arch: all' packages preventing installing on 64 bit system
    Fixed issue with GCC 4.7 whereas .bmp files would not load properly
    Fixed build issue with ARM build
    Fixed build issue with big endian (PPC) builds
    Fixed broken HTTP protocol
    Fixed debugger breakpoint line number issues
    Fixed missing visual color in color drop box
    Fixed wrong font transform and kerning when using different attributes for the same face
    Fixed unlocking a mutex in runtime library (GuiApplication) when it has not been locked
    In IDE and Compiler, fixed buffer overflows in local char arrays
    In FileDialog, reordered if condition to avoid UMR
    In runtime library object system, resolved conditional jumps based on uninitialized values reported by Valgrind
    In Compiler, fixed crashes by properly reinitializing members of union inside Specifier class
    In Compiler, fixed bad memory access in lexer showing up in Valgrind

 -- Jerome St-Louis <jerstlouis@gmail.com>  Mon, 28 Jan 2013 06:48:00 -0500

